in the case of the orcs is also a matter of record.  Whatever his
personal beliefs, he was not comfortable with the idea that Orcs,
Elves and men were morally equivalent, and he was also not comfortable
with the idea that Orcs were born evil because their ancestors made
the wrong choice.
